<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ómir kitabynda esimim</title>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.C        G        Am
 Ómir kitabynda esimim
.     G          C
 Saǵan alǵys aıtamyn.
.C       G          Am
 Máńgilikte bir ózgeris,
.      G          C
 Júrek jyryn jyrladym
.F             G
 Jańa ánin arnadym.

[C1]
.  F      G         Am
    Jeldiń samalyndasyń,
.  Am     G         C
    Kúnniń shýaǵyndasyń!
.  F      G           Am
    Bulbul qustyń áninde,
.  Am    G         C
   Teńiz tolqynyndasyń!
   O, Qudaıym, Sen meniń júregimdesiń!

[V2]
 Aǵady ómir ózeni,
 Máńgilik ómir sýy.
 Ár tamshy sýy Senimen,
 Ótkizgen ár kúnderim
 Tek úmitpen, senimmen!</lyrics>
<author>Nur</author>
</song>